<$fill $name="body">

!! Content type

|!Type |!Purpose |
|`text/x-frontmattered-markdown` |Tiddler type ‚Äî triggers YAML frontmatter serialization on save |
|`application/x-tiddler-frontmatter` |Internal disk type ‚Äî used by save pipeline patches |

!! YAML field handling

|!Field |!YAML format |
|`tags` |Array: `tags:\n  - tag1\n  - tag2` |
|`list` |Array: `list:\n  - item1\n  - item2` |
|`title` |Excluded from frontmatter (derived from tiddler title) |
|`text` |Excluded from frontmatter (appears after `---` closing delimiter) |
|All other fields |Scalar: `field-name: value` |

!! Frontmatter format

```
---
tags:
  - tag1
  - tag2
custom-field: value
type: text/x-frontmattered-markdown
---

Markdown body text here
```

!! Restart rules

|!Change |!Restart? |
|`startup.js` |Yes |
|`deserializer.js` |Yes |
|`parser.js` |Yes |
|`yaml.js` |Yes |
|New `.md` files added to tiddlers/ |No (filesystem-watcher picks them up) |

</$fill>
</$transclude>
